event.logging

Class ApprovalEventAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • event.logging.ApprovalEventAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventAction, HasOutcome

    public class ApprovalEventAction
extends java.lang.Object
implements EventAction, HasOutcome
    This type describes an approval (or rejection) event in a workflow, e.g a workflow where a more privileged user is required to approve the work of another user.

    Java class for Approval complex type.
